// https://www.shadertoy.com/view/ftyBDc city grid by jt
// based on https://www.shadertoy.com/view/ftcfWf Asymmetric Blocks SDF

// Thinking about interesting semi-regular/random structures for procedural city layouts.
// This one combines two rotated copies of https://www.shadertoy.com/view/ftcfWf]Asymmetric Blocks SDF with xor.
// The cells could be blocks or parks (flip sdf).

